{"tid":627593,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"程班長","createTime":"2018-04-13T06:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T11:20:07.000Z","uid":181719,"like":5,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"27e875cabf3291a2e564776ecb9a23bcad399910","tid":627593,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:17:54.000Z","msg":"呢間基本上真係無人不識嘅，只係想讚吓佢水準真係一直都keep到。牛肉係腍甜，有少少調味，唔係用牛展片交行貨。湯底我次次都係食紅燒，夠濃但食完唔特別口渴，證明味精唔重，而且夠熱，夠熱同埋夠熱。麵夠爽口同埋香口，仲有鋪面啲酸菜冇怪味（冇怪味已經好好）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/141643_9483a0c356f014cf20d8a4575dfae2d7.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F141643_9483a0c356f014cf20d8a4575dfae2d7.jpeg&h=003a113c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有，開咗咁耐價錢亦都keep到50路，其實真係良心食店黎。<br />\n所以雖然接近每個月去一次，我都只係食到個紅燒牛肉麵，因為真係唔捨得唔食，但食完又冇quota食其他野。好喇，為咗多樣野出po，嗌多咗個哇包，裏面夾住豬腩肉餡，但係除咗夠大個之外，冇乜特別。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/141659_586cbbfbe8eea99563725f4e17843f07.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F141659_586cbbfbe8eea99563725f4e17843f07.jpeg&h=3dbdb523&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/141706_999bb2464a47d92bb34c4a694da85479.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F141706_999bb2464a47d92bb34c4a694da85479.jpeg&h=293285a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc0bfa3485f1a39ee86b4a5b7c48d43215e818f9","tid":627593,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:21:17.000Z","msg":"負皮嘅巴打講吓佢有咩差，交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd38fb8c9e41be0ce18703816e868bdfdd84f6fb","tid":627593,"uid":50144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:44:01.000Z","msg":"牛肉麵食清燉是常識吧？"},{"pid":"1eb793668b1939e5006732d3b325e28f7563f06f","tid":627593,"uid":162567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:45:49.000Z","msg":"你食開精液?"},{"pid":"1b4ad604ce36d004a6e8851acae6800e806e12e9","tid":627593,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd38fb8c9e41be0ce18703816e868bdfdd84f6fb","tid":627593,"uid":50144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:44:01.000Z","msg":"牛肉麵食清燉是常識吧？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:49:57.000Z","msg":"都食過一次，但中意紅燒濃味多啲"},{"pid":"134b09f02063a5164e810720e327620d0806834f","tid":627593,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1eb793668b1939e5006732d3b325e28f7563f06f","tid":627593,"uid":162567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:45:49.000Z","msg":"你食開精液?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:50:34.000Z","msg":"未食過，點解會用精液黎類比佢碗麵？"},{"pid":"816b9a1196028703bc69dda844a871c407845187","tid":627593,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:53:52.000Z","msg":"台菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6628a306756d133c8c743d680e1f8dba85b9f51a","tid":627593,"uid":166568,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:54:55.000Z","msg":"琴晚去咗食佢地個魯肉飯<br />\n冇出面其他台灣野咁油咁膩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫咗杯冬瓜茶好好飲<br />\n隻味真係出面啲做唔到，食完仲買多咗杯拎走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9fc5ffe131c29c393ecd862bea0d7e1a81f7df5","tid":627593,"uid":90000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:57:53.000Z","msg":"見到都唔想食"},{"pid":"ff5a3c0b1402d9982d8ba4044b52b266ed1e7a0f","tid":627593,"uid":105888,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:59:14.000Z","msg":"喺台灣食開地道野食<br />\n就會知道程班長狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462b1f3222de1556d0aaa934dcb3c6c36b5b2d60","tid":627593,"uid":17492,"like":0,"dislike":0,